                  <item>
                    <para><unit_number><number>300</number><unit>nm</unit></unit_number> is not shown in the table. However, this wavelength is just a little shorter than the shortest wavelength in the violet range. Therefore <unit_number><number>300</number><unit>nm</unit></unit_number> is <emphasis effect="italics">ultraviolet</emphasis>.</para>
                  </item>
